Popular disc jockey, Cuppy has reacted to a call by a Twitter user asking her to get a man that will impregnate her. The Twitter user, Daniel Jackson, found the idea of Cuppy referring to her pets as kids quite unsettling. He proposed the entertainer gets a man to impregnate her so that she can have a real child while arguing being a single parent isn’t an anomaly. “@cuppymusic why don’t you just find a guy that’ll impregnate you then calling those pets your kids???…being a single mom isn’t a bad thing,” Daniel tweeted.   Toyin Abraham, Mercy Aigbe, others solicits fund for ailing…     Ossai Osnanebi gifts wife 2022 Maserati on birthday     God punish me if I fail Nigerians- Yul Edochie   Quite amused by Daniel’s tweet, the billionaire heiress retweeted the same accompanied with several laughing emojis. Last month, DJ Cuppy applauded herself for being an extraordinary mother to her ‘sons’ (dogs), Dúdú and FünFün as she celebrated them on their first birthday. She shared photos where she rocked matching outfits with her ‘sons’ while expressing love for them.